title: Tezos Foundation backed Tezos Domains announces Gate.io listing with 500,000 $TED competition.
description: Gate.io has just announced a listing of Tezos Domains’ token (TED), shortly after announcing an ‘startup project free airdrop program’, with TED token meant to go live on the centralised exchange on 10th October 2023.
